Class saitMLS.problemDomain.Client extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

Serialized Fields

id

long id
Stores the client membership id number. Uniquely identifies the client with long integer value.

lastName

java.lang.String lastName
Stores the client's last name as string of maximum size of 20 characters.

firstName

java.lang.String firstName
Stores the client's first name as string of maximum size of 20 characters.

address

java.lang.String address
Stores the client's current address as string of maximum size of 50 characters.

postalCode

java.lang.String postalCode
Stores the client's current postal code as string of maximum size of 7 characters.

phoneNumber

java.lang.String phoneNumber
Stores the client's current phone number as string of maximum size of 14 characters in the following format (403) 222-5555.

activeStatus

boolean activeStatus
Stores the active status of this record in the random access file database of clients. If the client's active status holds true the client is active. If client's active status is false then the client's record is deleted.

clientType

char clientType
Stores the client type of this customer as to whether they are a residential (R) or commercial (C) client.

Class saitMLS.problemDomain.Property extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

Serialized Fields

id

long id
Unique identifier for each property. Self generated field. When adding a property enter 0 the id will be calculated. For searching the id may be specified to find a unique record.

legalDescription

java.lang.String legalDescription
A String containing the legal description of the property has a maximum length of 20 characters

address

java.lang.String address
A String containing the address of the property that is offered for sale. Maximum length of 80 characters

quadrant

java.lang.String quadrant
A String indicating the quadrant in which the property is located Valid values are NW, NE, SW, SE

zone

java.lang.String zone
A String representing the zoning laws applied to the property, Valid values are R1, R2, R3, R4, I1, I2, I3, I4

askingPrice

double askingPrice
A double representing the price that is being ask for the property

comments

java.lang.String comments
A String containing additional comments regarding the property. Maximum of 200 characters.
